Author: Alexbt
Title: ðŸ”¥[Pre-ICO]âœ… ArtPro - The Art of blockchain - Join Whitelistâœ…
Body: How ArtPro Separates Real Art From The Fake    ArtProâ€™s Provenance Solution ArtPro is a peer-to-peer marketplace connecting the buyers and sellers of art, fortified by a verification system which ensures the legitimacy of the artwork on sale. The Pro in ArtPro stands for provenance, referring to the â€˜chain of titleâ€™. To explain this term for a non-art audience, this is the record of documentation which supports the origins, ownership and authenticity of any piece of artwork. Since the blockchain is an immutable, unchangeable ledger, it lends itself perfectly to store this kind of information, ensuring prospective buyers that the chain and record have not been altered. It is imperative, therefore, that the information which finds its way onto the blockchain ledger is accurate in the first place.  For this to happen, three things must be confirmed: the identity of the seller, the authenticity of the piece, and that the piece in question is the same as the one recorded on the blockchain. So letâ€™s look at how ArtPro can achieve these three things.  https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/how-artpro-separates-real-art-from-fake-oliver-hams/

Title: ðŸ”¥[Pre-ICO]âœ… ArtPro - The Art of blockchain - Join Whitelistâœ…
Body: Hey there!   Buyers can search for available work on this platform with the help of filters. Once they have chosen a piece, the provenance report is downloaded using the APT token and they can add it to their cart. Payment is made using ATP and once the checkout is complete, the token is locked into the smart contract. Once successful delivery of the art has been confirmed or inventoried in a secure vault, the payment is released to the vendor. Finally, feedback is left by both transacting parties for our reputation system.

Title: ðŸ”¥[Pre-ICO]âœ… ArtPro - The Art of blockchain - Join Whitelistâœ…
Body: ArtPro is not alone in thinking that blockchain technology might both help secure authenticity and streamline the operations of the market itself. However, it is perhaps the most broad-based of all of its competitors, reaching out to the largest and most varied audience. Luckily, it also understands the limitations of blockchain technology and other such technical solutions. Its value and its success will depend on both the quality of its technology and on the credibility and skills of what experts it manages to recruit. If those parts of its proposal work out, ArtPro could lead the art market into the 21st century.

Body: Why Weâ€™re Introducing You to Our Competitorsâ€¦    We know the headline may sound a little counterintuitive but do bear with us. Two of the things we care most about at ArtPro is openness and honesty. The pro in ArtPro is short for provenance; which in practical terms is a trail of documentation which supports the origins, ownership and authenticity of a piece. In the case of ArtPro, we will ensure provenance by leveraging blockchain technology to create an immutable, tamper-proof record of information supplied from verified and credible sources. Author: elitecstrike
Title: ðŸ”¥[Pre-ICO]âœ… ArtPro - The Art of blockchain - Join Whitelistâœ…
Body: An Introduction to ArtPro: â€œThe Art of Blockchainâ€    Discover more about ArtPro, a tokenized project planning to democratize the art world and bring collectible artworks to the masses.  Welcome to ArtPro, a platform that promises to be many things for many people. Upon its launch, ArtPro will variously be:  â— A go-to marketplace for private dealers and contemporary artists  â— A system to connect artists and buyers that eliminates intermediaries  â— A modern system for valuing, authenticating, and acquiring art  â— A solution to the provenance problem that combines blockchain technology with the wisdom of real-world experts  â— A means for newcomers to invest in collectible art with minimal entry requirements  â— The platform that drags the old-fashioned art world into the 21st century  Thereâ€™s moreâ€Šâ€”â€Šlots moreâ€Šâ€”â€Šbut thatâ€™s enough to be going on with. In the run-up to our token sale, weâ€™ll be delving into each element of the project in detail and explaining the reasoning behind each component.  Essentially, ArtPro aims to become the go-to marketplace for buying and selling art. Whether thatâ€™s to hang in your front room or to keep in a secure vault is your prerogative. If itâ€™s the latter, weâ€™ll provide you with the tools to do so, including a turnkey service through one of our fully insured custodial partners. If itâ€™s the former, ditto: weâ€™ll make the process as seamless as possible, including tools such as augmented reality (AR) to help you visualize artworks before you buy them, so you can find the perfect piece for your home.  And, underpinning it all, will be a dual token model that utilizes the attributes for which blockchain technology is renowned: ERC721 non-fungible tokens (NFTs) to represent and track every artwork listed on the ArtPro platform, and as the ArtPro Token APT, an ERC20 token that serves as the native currency and incentivization mechanism within the ArtPro ecosystem, which includes a desktop platform, mobile dApp, and eventually various third party integrations.  https://medium.com/artproplatform/an-introduction-to-artpro-the-art-of-blockchain-8999ed832bb8
